 <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cloud Meeting - Premium Video Meetings</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        .input-group {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .input-group-text {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px 0 0 5px;
        }

        .form-control {
            border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
        }

        .btn-outline-primary {
            border-color: #007bff;
            color: #007bff;
            border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-outline-primary:hover {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
        }

        hr {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h1>Premium Video Meetings. Now Free for Everyone.</h1>
                <p>We've re-engineered the service to make secure cloud meetings free and available for all.</p>
                <div class="my-4">
                    <a class="btn btn-primary new-meeting" href="/new-meeting" role="button">Start a New Meeting</a>
                    <form action="join-room" style="margin-left: 1rem;" method="POST">
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <span class="input-group-text">
                                <ion-icon name="planet-outline"></ion-icon>
                            </span>
                            <input name="room_id" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Enter a code or Link" aria-label="Recipient's username" aria-describedby="button-addon2">
                            <button class="btn btn-outline-primary" type="submit" id="button-addon2">Join</button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <hr>
                <p><a href="#" style="text-decoration: none;">Learn more about</a> Cloud Meeting</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card" style="box-shadow: 0 0 5px #b8b8b8;">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <img src="/images/ss.png" width="100%" class="rounded" alt="Meeting Screenshot">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        &copy; 2023 Cloud Meeting. All Rights Reserved.
    </footer>
</body>
</html>












